  <data key="d15">st.ii-ii.q140.a002.ad1</data>
  <data key="d16">explicit_textual</data>
  <data key="d17">ance, not by reason of any greatness observable in them, but on account of the very nature of those virtues . Hence the need of precepts of patience and perseverance.</data>
  <data key="d18">reviewed_doctrinal</data>
  <data key="d19">patience | precept</data>
