<edge source="st.ii-ii.q137" target="concept.constancy_fortitude" id="edge.st.ii-ii.q137.treated_in.concept.constancy_fortitude">
  <data key="d6">edge.st.ii-ii.q137.treated_in.concept.constancy_fortitude</data>
  <data key="d7">st.ii-ii.q137</data>
  <data key="d8">II-II q.137 — Perseverance</data>
  <data key="d9">question</data>
  <data key="d10">treated_in</data>
  <data key="d11">concept.constancy_fortitude</data>
  <data key="d12">Constancy</data>
  <data key="d13">habit</data>
  <data key="d14">ann.st-ii-ii-q137-treated-in-concept-constancy-fortitude-st-ii-ii-q137-a003-resp</data>
  <data key="d15">st.ii-ii.q137.a003.resp</data>
  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">Perseverance and constancy agree as to end, since it belongs to both to persist firmly in some good : but they differ as to those things which make it difficult to persist in good . Because the virtue of pe</data>
  <data key="d18">reviewed_structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d19">perseverance</data>
</edge>
<edge source="st.ii-ii.q137" target="concept.perseverance_virtue" id="edge.st.ii-ii.q137.treated_in.concept.perseverance_virtue">
  <data key="d6">edge.st.ii-ii.q137.treated_in.concept.perseverance_virtue</data>
  <data key="d7">st.ii-ii.q137</data>
  <data key="d8">II-II q.137 — Perseverance</data>
  <data key="d9">question</data>
  <data key="d10">treated_in</data>
  <data key="d11">concept.perseverance_virtue</data>
  <data key="d12">Perseverance (Fortitude Part)</data>
  <data key="d13">virtue</data>
  <data key="d14">ann.st-ii-ii-q137-treated-in-concept-perseverance-virtue-st-ii-ii-q137-a001-resp</data>
  <data key="d15">st.ii-ii.q137.a001.resp</data>
  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">e other moderates fear and daring in connection with dangers of death (which also is something difficult in itself), so perseverance is a special virtue , since it consists in enduring delays in the above or other virtuous deeds , so far as necessity requires.</data>
  <data key="d18">reviewed_structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d19">perseverance</data>
</edge>
