  <data key="d15">st.ii-ii.q139.a001.resp</data>
  <data key="d16">explicit_textual</data>
  <data key="d17">idence of this is infused into the mind by the Holy Ghost Who expels any fear of the contrary. It is in this sense that fortitude is reckoned a gift of the Holy Ghost . For it has been stated above ( I-II:68:1-2 ) that the gifts regard the motion of the mind by the Holy Ghost .</data>
  <data key="d18">reviewed_structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d19">gift</data>
</edge>
